Technical requirements
Ability to add a new “reminder” (max 30 chars) for a user entered day and time.
Display reminders on the calendar view in the correct time order.
Ability to edit reminders – including changing text, day and time & colour.
Ability to delete reminders.
Calendar should be responsive.
Use a CSS preprocessor like LESS
Provide a readme with an instruction how to install your application
You should you React + redux.

Bonus (optional)
Writing unit tests for the available features will be considered as a big plus (Jest, Enzyme).
Find a nice way to handle the displaying of the reminders, when multiple appear on the same date.
Allow the user to select a colour when creating a reminder and display it appropriately.
Prev / Next month (or day) functionality
Use date-fns for dates or other simple library (avoid using moment.js).
Drag&drop ability to sort reminders.
Using react hooks.
